habits and helps cultivate self-learning ability. The research results can be utilized as a crucial reference for engineering education reform and provide a reliable model for the sustainable development of education.', 'year': 2023, 'referenceCount': 59, 'citationCount': 2, 'journal': {'name': 'Sustainability'}, 'citationStyles': {'bibtex': '@Article{Li2023ApplicationOS,
